'''''Ed Greenwood Presents Elminster's Forgotten Realms''''' by [[Ed Greenwood]] is a sourcebook for the ''[[Forgotten Realms]]'' setting released in the fall of 2012.

{{Quote|''"Tis the besetting doom of [[humans]] that they forget. This was in fact why thy mother or a teacher advised thee - just as sages in the Realms advise [[Faerûn]]ians - "Write it down." Well, now we have done just that. "Twas about time, too!"''

''With those words, [[Elminster]] of [[Shadowdale]] welcomes you to Faerûn and invites you to join [[Ed Greenwood]], the creator of the [[Forgotten Realms]] setting, on a guided tour of his famous world. This tome also presents never-before-seen notes and previously unpublished material written by Ed many years ago, when he and Faerûn were both younger.''}}

